#: ../../docs/frontpage.md:9
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you want this index page to be hidden from site visitors, a Global "
"Administrator can select one public site on your installation to which "
"visitors will be redirected when they navigate to your base URL "
"(`yourdomain.net/omekas/`). To do so:"
msgstr ""
"Si vous voulez que ce site soit caché des visiteurs, vous pouvez utiliser"
" le [paramètre site par défaut](admin/settings.md#global-settings) pour "
"sélectionner un site public sur votre installation vers lequel les "
"visiteurs seront redirigés quand ils navigueront vers votre URL de base "
"(`votredomaine.net/omekas`)"

#: ../../docs/frontpage.md:11
msgid "Go to Settings (the gear icon), then the General tab."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/frontpage.md:12
msgid ""
"Under the \"Default site\" option, use the dropdown menu to select one of"
" your current sites."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/frontpage.md:13
msgid ""
"To remove a selected site and revert back to the index page, click the "
"small \"X\" on the right side of the dropdown."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/frontpage.md:15
msgid ""
"You can customize a branded site index for your installation by creating "
"a site, creating a page, and then using the [\"List of sites\" page "
"block](sites/site_pages.md#page-blocks) to generate a list of all the "
"sites in the installation. Then, use the \"Default site\" option to point"
" to that site."
msgstr ""

